At the moment, it is possible to preview images and pdf attachments in JIRA. However, it is not possible for Word documents.

If the business requirement requires word documents attached to issues often, and these documents contain useful / further information to be read by staff when acting on an issue, I believe preview for Word documents would be great. If these files are viewed multiple times, they're being downloaded multiple times and will fill up the downloads folders. It's not stopping user from working, but it might have an impact on user morale/happiness/frustration.

