When logging work, there is a restriction setting at the bottom that limits the users that can view and edit the work log. It would be preferable to be able to default this setting to something other than All Users so that default visibility of work log entries could be controlled.

!image-2017-03-20-15-15-33-943.png!  

The goal here is to allow work log entries to be securely controlled. Previous issues have been logged asking for a View Work Logs permission to control visibility (which would also suffice) but since it appears that Atlassian is not going to deliver on that type of functionality (issues closed with a Won't Do), then we believe that a default should be able to be set for the functionality that is already present.

